sources.title: Beehive Kandu1975
sources.description: Synopsis Recently have been released from jail, Ebi makes a bet with his Friend that he goes and drinks in seven bars without even paying any money. Cast: Reza Karam Rezai, Ezatallah Ramezanifar, Davoud Rashidi, Parvin Solaymani, Behrouz Vossoughi Cinematography: Hamid Mojtahedi, Fereydun Reypoor
